  <h>fad</h>

  <section>
    <h>dependents</h>
    <section>
      <h>specifier</h>
      <p><xl>
          <li>
            <gd>Dé tha ceàrr air a’ ghille seo? Tha a cheann goirt. An robh e anns an sgoil an
              diugh? Cha robh, bha e anns an taigh fad <m>an latha</m>.</gd>
            <tr>What is wrong with this boy? His head is sore. Was he in the school today? No, he
              was in the house all day long.</tr>
            <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
          </li>
          <li>
            <gd>An robh an clachair ag obair air a’ bhalla fad <m>an latha</m> an dé? Bha.</gd>
            <tr>Was the mason working on the wall all day yesterday? Yes, he was.</tr>
            <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
          </li>
        </xl></p>
    </section>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h>uses</h>
    <section>
      <h>modifier</h>
      <p><xl>
          <li>
            <gd>Dé tha ceàrr air a’ ghille seo? Tha a cheann goirt. An robh e anns an sgoil an
              diugh? Cha robh, bha e anns an taigh <m>fad</m> an latha.</gd>
            <tr>What is wrong with this boy? His head is sore. Was he in the school today? No, he
              was in the house all day long.</tr>
            <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
          </li>
          <li>
            <gd>An robh an clachair ag obair air a’ bhalla <m>fad</m> an latha an dé? Bha.</gd>
            <tr>Was the mason working on the wall all day yesterday? Yes, he was.</tr>
            <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
          </li>
        </xl></p>
    </section>
  </section>



