    <xl>
      <li>2939</li>
      <li>2941</li>
    </xl>
    <p>See also: <strong><a href="?gd=nuair">nuair</a></strong>
      <en>when</en>.</p>
    <p><strong>fhad ’s a</strong> sometimes has conditional force in this kind of construction –</p>
    <xl>
      <li>3299</li>
    </xl>
    <p>See also: <strong>ma</strong>, <strong>nam</strong>, <strong>mura</strong>.</p>
  </box>

